reviewText: Thanks for the speedy wonderful service! One of the best collections available for all the Vicente Fernandez fans of the world.
These are really some nice movies, remind me of the days when I would sit around the house on a sunday afternoon and watch them on TV.

This volume contains the four movies:

1. El Arracadas
2. Juan Armenta El Repatriado
3. La Ley Del Monte
4. Enter Compadres Te Veas

 I am probably biased as I am a Vicente fan. This is a good set. It is one of the groups I enjoy most. It was one of the first group I viewed when I began collecting Vicente volumes and I definitely think it is a good price for a four-pack to see if you, too, will be a big Vicente fan.
